name: Ahegao
description:
The one you always needed.

I literally had to manually crop each images in this one and it sucks.

-Satyam

Needs tons of triggers because I made it so.

Use weight between 0.4-0.9, even 1.0 is better but since this is 128 DIM it starts adding noise at 1.0.

Every image in the dataset was manually gathered and it was hard to find images with the exact ahegao face. So I had to go through Pixiv premium in which I found an artist which only creates Ahegao thus if you put weight 2.0 you will see his arts but its all messed. I also had to go through doujins to get the Ahegao face so you might even see greyscale and monochrome images.

You can support me on KoFi and Patreon

Would appreciate your reviews and Image Generations.
